<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <title>Taepyung Company Profile - 10</title>

  <style>
    @page {
      size: A4 landscape;
      margin: 0;
    }

    :root {
      --green: #387040;
      --light-green: #70C088;
      --cream: #F7F5EF;
      --black: #111111;
      --gray: #777777;
      --line: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html,
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: Pretendard, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif;
      background: #d9d9d9;
      color: var(--black);
      -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
      print-color-adjust: exact;
    }

    .page {
      position: relative;
      width: 297mm;
      height: 210mm;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20mm 22mm 16mm;
      background: var(--cream);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* Header */
    .topbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      height: 14mm;
      margin-bottom: 18mm;
    }

    .logo-area {
      width: 42mm;
      height: 12mm;
      border: 1px dashed rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.35);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .logo-area img {
      width: 100%;
      max-height: 100%;
      object-fit: contain;
      display: block;
    }

    .doc-label {
      padding-top: 1mm;
      font-size: 8px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      color: var(--gray);
      text-align: right;
    }

    /* Main Layout */
    .layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.78fr 1.22fr;
      gap: 20mm;
      height: 128mm;
    }

    .left,
    .right {
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .left {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      font-size: 8.5px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 9mm;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 30px;
      line-height: 1.16;
      letter-spacing: -0.065em;
      font-weight: 760;
    }

    .lead {
      margin-top: 12mm;
      max-width: 82mm;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.85;
      letter-spacing: -0.035em;
      color: #222;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .summary-box {
      width: 82mm;
      border-top: 1.5px solid var(--green);
      padding-top: 5.5mm;
    }

    .summary-title {
      font-size: 25px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.06em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 780;
      margin-bottom: 4mm;
    }

    .summary-text {
      max-width: 70mm;
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: #444;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    /* Facility Visual */
    .facility-hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
      gap: 5mm;
      height: 47mm;
      margin-bottom: 5mm;
    }

    .facility-image {
      position: relative;
      background: rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.16);
      overflow: hidden;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.72);
      font-size: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .facility-image img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
    }

    .facility-info {
      padding: 6mm;
      background: var(--green);
      color: #fff;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .facility-label {
      font-size: 7.5px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      font-weight: 800;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .facility-title {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: -0.06em;
      font-weight: 780;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .facility-desc {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 9.5px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    /* Equipment Cards */
    .equipment-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 5mm;
      height: 42mm;
      margin-bottom: 5mm;
    }

    .equipment-card {
      padding: 6mm;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.68);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .equipment-label {
      font-size: 7.5px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 800;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .equipment-title {
      margin: 5mm 0 3mm;
      font-size: 15.5px;
      line-height: 1.2;
      letter-spacing: -0.055em;
      font-weight: 760;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .equipment-desc {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 9.2px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: #444;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .equipment-count {
      margin-top: 4mm;
      padding-top: 3mm;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.18);
      font-size: 8.2px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 800;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    /* Operation System */
    .operation-area {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 5mm;
      height: 34mm;
      padding: 5mm;
      background: rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.16);
    }

    .operation-item {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.16);
      padding-right: 5mm;
    }

    .operation-item:last-child {
      border-right: 0;
      padding-right: 0;
    }

    .operation-index {
      font-size: 7.5px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .operation-title {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 13.5px;
      line-height: 1.25;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      color: #111;
      font-weight: 760;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .operation-desc {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 8.8px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: #444;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      position: absolute;
      left: 22mm;
      right: 22mm;
      bottom: 9mm;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-end;
      font-size: 7.5px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      color: var(--gray);
    }

    .footer-logo {
      font-weight: 750;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: var(--green);
    }

    .page-no {
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: rgba(56, 112, 64, 0.65);
    }

    @media print {
      html,
      body {
        width: 297mm;
        height: 210mm;
        background: #fff;
      }

      .page {
        margin: 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <section class="page">

    <header class="topbar">
      <div class="logo-area">
        LOGO
        <!-- 로고 넣을 때 -->
        <!-- <img src="assets/taepyung-logo-green.svg" alt="Taepyung"> -->
      </div>

      <div class="doc-label">
        Company Profile<br />
        Ver. 2025-V1
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="layout">

      <section class="left">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Production System</div>

          <h1>
            전 공정 자동화 설비로<br />
            안정적인 생산 시스템을<br />
            구축했습니다
          </h1>

          <p class="lead">
            태평제지는 2022년 12월 이천 공장 이전과 함께
            전 공정 완전 자동화 설비로 교체하며 생산 안정성과 운영 효율성을 강화했습니다.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="summary-box">
          <div class="summary-title">Automated</div>
          <div class="summary-text">
            주요 생산라인의 자동화 설비와 물류 운영 체계를 바탕으로
            전국 공급에 대응할 수 있는 생산 기반을 갖추고 있습니다.
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="right">

        <div class="facility-hero">
          <div class="facility-image">
            FACTORY IMAGE
            <!-- <img src="assets/factory.jpg" alt="이천 공장"> -->
          </div>

          <div class="facility-info">
            <div class="facility-label">Icheon Factory</div>

            <h3 class="facility-title">
              이천 공장 이전과 함께<br />
              생산라인 자동화 구축
            </h3>

            <p class="facility-desc">
              공장 이전을 계기로 생산 설비를 정비하고,
              주요 제품군의 안정적인 제조를 위한 자동화 기반을 마련했습니다.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="equipment-grid">

          <div class="equipment-card">
            <div>
              <div class="equipment-label">Line 01</div>
              <h3 class="equipment-title">두루마리 화장지 설비</h3>
              <p class="equipment-desc">
                로그와인더, 커팅기, 오버래핑기, 케이스패커 등 생산 공정 설비 보유
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="equipment-count">장폭 1대</div>
          </div>

          <div class="equipment-card">
            <div>
              <div class="equipment-label">Line 02</div>
              <h3 class="equipment-title">점보롤 설비</h3>
              <p class="equipment-desc">
                점보롤 M/C, 점보롤 포장기, 파렛타이즈 듀얼형 등 대용량 제품 생산 설비 보유
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="equipment-count">장폭 2대</div>
          </div>

          <div class="equipment-card">
            <div>
              <div class="equipment-label">Line 03</div>
              <h3 class="equipment-title">페이퍼타올 설비</h3>
              <p class="equipment-desc">
                인터폴더, 엠보싱, 커팅기, 포장기 등 페이퍼타올 생산 공정 설비 보유
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="equipment-count">장폭 2대</div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <div class="operation-area">

          <div class="operation-item">
            <div class="operation-index">01</div>
            <h3 class="operation-title">실시간 재고 파악</h3>
            <p class="operation-desc">
              입·출고 흐름을 관리하며 안정적인 공급을 지원합니다.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="operation-item">
            <div class="operation-index">02</div>
            <h3 class="operation-title">전국 배송 체계</h3>
            <p class="operation-desc">
              전국 어디든 빠르게 배송할 수 있는 물류 체계를 운영합니다.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="operation-item">
            <div class="operation-index">03</div>
            <h3 class="operation-title">최적 배차 운영</h3>
            <p class="operation-desc">
              합배송 등 효율적인 배차를 통해 물류비 최적화를 추구합니다.
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>

      </section>

    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="footer-logo">TAE PYEONG PAPER</div>
      <div class="page-no">10</div>
    </footer>

  </section>

</body>
</html>
